title: Studio SONO Amazing location 4th floor
posting_body: ['Studio Apartment top floor corner  unit over looking Washington Street.', 'Elevator building.', '420 square feet.', 'living /sleeping room with murphy bed that folds up when not in use.', 'Kitchen with  lots of storage and island counter top for dining.', 'Refrigerator freezer.', 'Furnishings  included.', 'Bathroom with tub shower.', '2 large clothing closets.', 'no washer or dryer.', 'laundry around the corner.', 'Walking to SONO train, SONO Mall, dozens of restaurants, pubs, night life.', 'Shopping.', 'Must have reliable income and excellent references.', 'First , Last and one Months security at lease signing.', 'Electric Heat and AC additional.', 'Available covered parking garage near by for additional fee .', '$1200 month year lease or $2200 month to month with maid service.', 'Available September 1.', 'Email for additional info and application.', 'Viewing by appointment.', 'pets not allowed by the condo association.', 'I have been out of town with out internet, if you emailed me and are still interested, please send me an email  again.', 'thanks']
